node.text:
Our 12 Days of Giving starts now! We’re kicking off the giving by helping you bring the essence of Pure Salt to your home this holiday season! Like with any of our projects, that means leaning in to design that is cozy, fresh, clean (in every sense), and inspired to create a natural atmosphere where cherished memories are made. We think every home needs a little bit of:
- cozy music
- candles & scents
- calm & clean decor
- candles, candles, and more candles!
Check out our stories today to learn more about how we use each element to infuse the season with some Pure Salt magic ✨// 🎬: @trevorfilm

node.text: Dipping our toes into video content with @618studios to tell you a little bit more about who we are and what makes us Pure Salt!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors in Rancho Mission Viejo. May be an image of 2 people and bedroom.

node.text: Talk about a dream come true! We have exciting news and can’t contain ourselves any longer—we have quite literally been dreaming of this since we founded Pure Salt—we are thrilled to say that our long await bedding collection is finally here! And it will be launching this Wednesday! If you know us and Pure Salt you know cozy comfy and beautiful go hand in hand as our design point of view, and these bedding pieces are so soft and so unique, we hope you love them as much as we do 🤍 // 📷: @vlentine

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors in Newport Beach, California. May be an image of living room.

node.text: Arches and tabletops—plenty of opportunities for styling all our favorites 🤩 our Romana console is is ultra long and anchors a seating area while offering storage solutions as well as extended surface books, beads, and beautiful greens // 📷: @vlentine

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors in Los Gatos, California. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: Swooning and smiling over this cutie pool bath at our #losgatosproject ✨ the spindly metal legs of the vanity mixed with the natural textures of the woven mirror and white oak picture frame complement and contrast one another in the best beachy way and even make this toilet look good! // 📷: @vlentine

node.text:
The workstation of the #threearchbayproject kitchen up close... and the luxe seating peninsula zoomed out for lots of clean views ✨ // 📷: @jessicaalexander

node.text: Heading into the weekend well rested and giddy for something new, exciting and very cozy coming to the shoppe next week! Any guesses what it could be? 👀 // 📷: @vlentine

node.text: With a mix of clever cabinetry solutions and open shelving, the kitchen at our #losgatosproject has ample storage as well as opportunity for styling! We are huge lovers of functional decor, and these shelves were the perfect place to arrange cookbooks, cutting boards, and lots of ceramics for a layered look // 📷: @vlentine

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors in Newport Beach, California. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: We are big believers that you can and should maximize every available inch of your home for function—team no wasted space! For this teeny nook off the stairs in the entry of our #portstreetsproject we added a simple bench to set a purse or put on some shoes. Stacking it with a few pillows and adding some green makes this small utility space feel grand and purposeful and very very sweet ✨ // 📷: @vlentine

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pure Salt Interiors on August 05, 2021. May be an image of sofa and living room.

node.text:
Looking for more ways to refresh your home? We've got sale on sale with our summer sale favorites on an additional 10% off with code SALEONSALE! Head to the shoppe to see all the goodies, then find your favorite deal to take home! // 📷: @vlentine

node.text: Our vintage maps from our Certified Original collection are such a fun pop of history, texture, and a great conversation starter! We love adding them to gallery walls, but think they make the cutest countertop and shelf decor too! it feels so casual and chic to lean these pieces up against the wall and let them shine and speak for themselves 😍 // 📷: @vlentine

node.text: Today feels like a day to enjoy the great outdoors ☀ and the backyard lounge at our #portstreetsproject is calling our name with it's cozy and plush pillows and fun fire pit! This space was one of the first where we could layer up all our outdoor pillows—the result looks so cozy and pretty, and with the durable weather-proofed fabrics, we know this family will be able to enjoy them for years to come // 📷: @vlentine
